title: Photostat, "Immeuble de Rapport Construit a Paris avec les Fontes de St. Dizier", 1885–1930
medium: Photostat and black ink on paper
signed: Lower right in black ink: Papier, Gavure et Impression L. GEISLER
inscribed: Top in black ink: IMMOBLIERE DE RAPPORT CONSTRUIT A PARIS AVES LES FONTES DE ST. DIZIER
description: A design for an apartment building in which the central panel of the building has three windows, and the other two side panels have two.

tombstone.epitaph:
Photostat, "Immeuble de Rapport Construit a Paris avec les Fontes de St. Dizier", 1885–1930.
1885–1930. Photostat and black ink on paper. Gift of Mme. Hector Guimard. 1950-66-56.
